name: backend-design
description: "Backend implementation patterns: API endpoint design
  (REST/GraphQL/gRPC), database schema design (PostgreSQL/MongoDB/Redis),
  caching implementation (Cache-Aside/Write-Through), authentication flows
  (OAuth2/JWT/mTLS), observability instrumentation (OpenTelemetry), and backend
  testing strategies. Trigger when designing API endpoints, database schemas,
  caching layers, auth flows, or planning backend testing."
version: 1.0.0
emoji: 🛠️
